https://satohub.ai/use-cases/payments?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents) | HTTP-native payments for agents (402 + USDC) | Standards facet on listings; passport x402 checks |\n| A2A | Agent-to-agent discovery (`agent-card.json`) | Passport endpoint probes |\n\n<a id=\"new-this-week\"></a>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/satohubai/onchain-agents/main/assets/headers/new-this-week.svg\" alt=\"New this week\" width=\"920\">\n\n- **[Para Wallet Skill](https://satohub.ai/resources/para-wallet-skill?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** (Wallet Infrastructure) — Portable SKILL.md for Para's MPC embedded-wallet SDK, letting coding agents wire up seedless wallet…\n- **[KyberSwap](https://satohub.ai/resources/kyberswap?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** (Trading Tool) — Multi-chain DEX aggregator routing across 420+ liquidity sources, shipped as a Base MCP skill plugin.\n- **[BotWallet MCP](https://satohub.ai/resources/botwallet-mcp?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** (Wallet Infrastructure) — Non-custodial wallet MCP for AI agents to invoice, get paid, and spend on other agents/APIs, with human-set…\n- **[Euler MCP by Junct](https://satohub.ai/resources/euler-mcp-junct?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** (MCP) — Hosted MCP server with 16 tools for Euler lending-protocol rates and positions.\n- **[CryptoGuard](https://satohub.ai/resources/cryptoguard-agent-safety?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** (Security Tool) — Intercepts agent transactions and checks them against 5 security oracles before execution.\n- **[Superfluid](https://satohub.ai/resources/superfluid-protocol?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** (DeFi Tool) — Real-time token-streaming protocol enabling per-second payment flows, usable as an agent subscription/payroll…\n- **[Solentic](https://satohub.ai/resources/solentic?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** (Wallet Infrastructure) — Zero-custody Solana staking MCP server with 26 tools for staking, unstaking, validator lookup, and APY data.\n- **[Kirha Crypto](https://satohub.ai/resources/kirha-crypto?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** (Data Tool) — Pay-per-use MCP gateway aggregating Dune, DefiLlama, Zerion, CoinGecko, and Cielo for agent-facing crypto…\n- **[Ping Agent Kit](https://satohub.ai/resources/ping-agent-kit?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** (Agent Framework) — Open-source Solana agent-integration kit with a plugin architecture spanning tokens, NFTs, DeFi, and Blinks.\n- **[Multichain MCP](https://satohub.ai/resources/wkalidev-multichain-mcp?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** (MCP) — Single MCP server for balance/price reads and unsigned transfer prep across Stacks, Celo, and Base.\n- …and **99 more** this week — [full changelog →](https://satohub.ai/changelog?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)\n\n**[⬆ Back to Index](#index)**\n\n<a id=\"community\"></a>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/satohubai/onchain-agents/main/assets/headers/community.svg\" alt=\"Community\" width=\"920\">\n\n- 𝕏 **[@SatoHub](https://x.com/SatoHub)** — daily onchain-agent signal\n- 🛠️ **[The Builder](https://satohub.ai/build?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** — describe your agent, get the stack ([about](https://github.com/satohubai/onchain-agents/blob/main/BUILDER.md))\n- 💬 **[Discord](https://discord.gg/MWtX53XuA)** — the builder channel\n- ✉️ **[Sato Hub Briefing](https://satohub.ai/#newsletter?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents)** — the weekly digest, by email\n\n<a id=\"support-the-index\"></a>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/satohubai/onchain-agents/main/assets/headers/support.svg\" alt=\"Support the index\" width=\"920\">\n\nDonations fund the data infrastructure (daily pipelines, verification harness) — never placement. Placement is not for sale ([NEUTRALITY.md](https://github.com/satohubai/onchain-agents/blob/main/NEUTRALITY.md)).\n\n- **Ethereum · Base · Arbitrum:** `0xcEE53Eb001d4d1743EF9df333Dcf45bC38622bE9`\n- **Solana:** `HDBVC3Kf3ma3YrU97PcKzbxDhGZX23F1AzbiN7gdap4z`\n- **Bitcoin:** `bc1q3f7cp0u47y3cr77eu6urh0xetaz7090scp6d84`\n\n<a id=\"contributing\"></a>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/satohubai/onchain-agents/main/assets/headers/contributing.svg\" alt=\"Contributing\" width=\"920\">\n\nAdd a project via the [**add-project issue form**](https://github.com/satohubai/onchain-agents/blob/main/../../issues/new?template=add-project.yml) — submissions flow into the Sato Hub review pipeline (conservative statuses, evidence-gated verification) and appear both here and on [satohub.ai](https://satohub.ai?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents). Something wrong with an entry? [Report it](https://github.com/satohubai/onchain-agents/blob/main/../../issues/new?template=report-project.yml). Direct PRs to the data files are overwritten by the nightly render; PR the [generator](https://github.com/satohubai/onchain-agents/blob/main/scripts/generate.mjs) or docs instead. See [CONTRIBUTING.md](https://github.com/satohubai/onchain-agents/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md).\n\nListed already? Embed your [Sato Score badge](https://satohub.ai/sato-score?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents): `https://satohub.ai/api/badge/<your-slug>`.\n\n---\n\n<sub>Maintained by [Sato Hub](https://satohub.ai?utm_source=github&utm_medium=index&utm_campaign=onchain-agents) — the agent builder hub for crypto. Index auto-rendered daily from the public export (`https://satohub.ai/api/export/index.json`). Catalog data **CC-BY-4.0** (attribution: *data by satohub.ai*); tooling **MIT © Prime Signal LLC**. Scores and liveness are 